{"title":"MyCanyon Turns Custom Canyon Bike Dreams Into Reality","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mycanyon-custom-canyon-bike-dreams-turned-reality/","date":1740679457000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-header-1-1-1536x864.png\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>Canyon is finally making full custom happen, and it’s not just a color palette swap or a parts bin shuffle. <strong><a href=\"https://www.canyon.com/en-us/my-canyon-custom-bike/\">MyCanyon</a></strong> is here, and it’s bringing pro-level personalization, your pick of components, and stunning artwork to your dream build. Kicking off with the Aeroad CFR, this program pairs race-winning performance with jaw-dropping aesthetics (these paint jobs are awesome), including collaborations with world-class artists Felipe Pantone and Elena Salmistraro.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"8299\" height=\"5533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--jpg.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR art\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--jpg.webp 8299w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-art--768x512.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(All photos: Canyon)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s MyCanyon All About?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Forget cookie-cutter builds. MyCanyon lets you dial in the details—paint, fit, and spec—so you roll out on an Aeroad CFR that’s uniquely yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"8715\" height=\"5800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--jpg.webp 8715w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-close-up--768x511.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-1536x1025.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-blkwhit-768x512.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Aeroad CFR:</strong> The Same Frame The Pros Trust – This isn’t a watered-down, consumer-only model. The MyCanyon program starts with Canyon’s flagship Aeroad CFR. </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Seamless Customization</strong> – Canyon’s online configurator keeps things simple but powerful, letting you build your ride without getting lost in an endless parts list.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dialed Fit &amp; Function</strong> – Choose your bars, stem length, saddle, wheels, and drivetrain, and even slap your name on the frame for a true one-of-one experience.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Artistry Meets Speed</strong> – Canyon partnered with Pantone and Salmistraro to design some wild, eye-catching graphics—and they’re exclusive to MyCanyon.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Handcrafted Perfection</strong> – Each MyCanyon build gets the complete boutique treatment, with hand-painted frames and precision assembly in Canyon’s new Build Lab.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR in design\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-in-design--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Streamlined Customization: Three Key Choices</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Canyon keeps it clean—no analysis paralysis. Instead, MyCanyon delivers a curated experience across three main areas:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1904\" height=\"1428\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR beatue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue.webp 1904w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-beatue-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Aesthetics: Rideable Art</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Three fresh frame design collections push the boundaries of what a custom bike can be:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fabric Collection</strong> – Shimmering metallics and shifting pigments bring a futuristic, deep-space energy to the Aeroad.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Mano Collection</strong> – Hand-painted, one-of-a-kind designs inspired by the cosmos—each frame is 100% unique.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Opus Collection</strong> – The main event features exclusive designs from Felipe Pantone and Elena Salmistraro.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble-.png\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR color bubble\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble-.png 3840w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--297x167.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--1536x864.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--120x68.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--768x432.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--2048x1152.png 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-color-bubble--1200x675.png 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Fit: Pro-Approved Ergonomics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Get race-ready with cockpit choices that fine-tune your position. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Stems</strong> – Multiple length options to nail your reach.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Saddles</strong> – Selle Italia choices for endurance or aggressive race positioning.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side-.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side-.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR dark side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side-.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side--297x149.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side--1536x768.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side--120x60.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side--768x384.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-dark-side--2048x1024.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Function: Performance-First Spec</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pick your dream drivetrain, wheels, and finishing kit:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupsets:</strong> Shimano Dura-Ace Di2 or SRAM RED AXS</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels</strong>: ZIPP 454 NSW with Pirelli P-Zero RS or DT Swiss ARC 1100 with Continental GP5000s</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bars &amp; Stems:</strong> The award-winning PACE Bar, with dialed-in options for max aero gains.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint-.png\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR Elena paint\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint-.png 3840w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--297x167.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--1536x864.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--120x68.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--768x432.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--2048x1152.png 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-paint--1200x675.png 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Meet the Artists: The Opus Collection</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>MyCanyon goes beyond performance—these are collector-worthy machines designed by two of the most innovative artists today:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR Panton\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Panton--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Felipe Pantone</strong> – Known for his dynamic, digital-inspired visuals, Pantone’s frame design makes your bike look as fast as it rides.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1.png\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR Elena\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1.png 3840w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-297x167.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-120x68.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-768x432.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-2048x1152.png 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-Elena-1-1-1200x675.png 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Elena Salmistraro </strong>– A creative force who’s worked with Disney, Nike, and Apple, bringing her bold, kaleidoscopic style to Canyon’s speed machine.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark-.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark-.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR full dark\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark-.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark--297x149.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark--1536x768.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark--120x60.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark--768x384.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-full-dark--2048x1024.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Who’s Riding Them?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s not just us regular riders getting the MyCanyon treatment. Mathieu van der Poel, Jasper Philipsen, Kasia Niewiadoma, and Chloé Dygert are ready to race on their custom-built Aeroad CFRs this season.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-white--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>How to Get Yours</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ordering your MyCanyon ride is straightforward and slick. Just hop on Canyon.com or the Canyon App, hit Custom Mode, and let the 3D Bike Visualizer guide you.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>See It Before You Buy – A full 3D render of your exact bike before checkout.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Real-Time Pricing &amp; Availability – No surprises, no delays.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Live Order Tracking – Watch your custom build progress from frame to finish.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Delivery? Your Call – Direct-to-door or pickup at one of Canyon’s 500+ service locations.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--jpg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"8568\" height=\"5702\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--jpg.webp\" alt=\"Mycanyon Custom Aeroad CFR red\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--jpg.webp 8568w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Mycanyon-Custom-Aeroad-CFR-red--768x511.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Global Rollout</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>USA: Available now</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Asia-Pacific: April 2025</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Europe &amp; Rest of World: By Summer 2025</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Price: Starting at $9,999</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.canyon.com/en-us/my-canyon-custom-bike/#section-product-grid\">www.canyon.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mycanyon-custom-canyon-bike-dreams-turned-reality/\">MyCanyon Turns Custom Canyon Bike Dreams Into Reality</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"869ff62ed576704f331effa661f0784bbd1eb4a0e3eac82ed21d8d5f7dfee63d","category":"Cycling"}